<xar:comment>Note: when using the image-resize tag, width percentage is calculated
                   on the size of the original image, not the size of the available
                   space.  This is why we are not using width="100%" here.
</xar:comment>
<xar:image-resize src="$file[fileId]" label="$title" width="500px" height="500px" constrain="true"/>
